  <sect2 role="package">
    <title>Introduction to Kdemultimedia</title>

    <para>This package aims to provide consistent, flexible, and useful
    interfaces. Applications, KParts, libraries, and plugins on the basis
    of Phonom (Amarok, K3B, Kaffeine, etc.).</para>

    &lfs67_checked;

